---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof for Dog Trainers — Client Testimonials That Fill Your Classes | SocialProof" description="Dog trainers: turn happy pet owners into your best marketing with automated testimonials. SocialProof helps you collect and display social proof that books more clients.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Dog Trainers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Dog owners are emotional buyers. They're desperate to solve a behavior problem, and they'll pick whoever looks most trustworthy and proven. SocialProof helps dog trainers capture heartfelt client success stories and turn them into the marketing that fills group classes and books private sessions.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Why dog trainers need testimonials more than most</h2>
      <p>A dog training client isn't just buying a service — they're trusting you with their relationship with their dog. The stakes feel high. They've probably already tried YouTube videos and failed. When they land on your website, they need to see that your method worked for other dogs like theirs.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Testimonials that name the specific behavior problem solved ("Max used to bite our guests...") are worth ten times more than generic praise. SocialProof makes it easy to collect exactly that kind of specific, story-driven feedback.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Testimonials that book dog training sessions</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Problem → solution:</strong> "Bella pulled so hard on leash I dreaded walks. After 4 sessions she heels perfectly."</li>
        <li><strong>Behavior transformation:</strong> "Our dog was reactive to other dogs. She's a completely different dog after 6 weeks."</li>
        <li><strong>The trainer's approach:</strong> "She never used fear or punishment — just positive methods that actually stuck."</li>
        <li><strong>Specific results:</strong> "Rocky now sits and stays reliably. We can have guests over without chaos."</li>
        <li><strong>Family peace restored:</strong> "Our kids can finally play in the backyard without getting knocked over."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for your training business</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Add the widget</strong> to your homepage and program pages — no technical skills required.</li>
        <li><strong>After completing a program</strong>, send clients your SocialProof link to share their story.</li>
        <li><strong>Clients share in their own words</strong> — no survey forms, no login, just a simple text box.</li>
        <li><strong>Approve the good ones</strong> and they instantly appear on your site.</li>
        <li><strong>Organize by program</strong> — show puppy class testimonials near your puppy page, reactive dog testimonials near that program, etc.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Works for all training formats</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Puppy foundation classes</li>
        <li>Basic obedience (group & private)</li>
        <li>Reactive dog & aggression rehabilitation</li>
        <li>Board and train programs</li>
        <li>Service dog & therapy dog training</li>
        <li>Virtual / remote training sessions</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background:#fdf4ff;border:1px solid #e9d5ff;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;font-style:italic;color:#6b21a8;">
          "I put SocialProof on my reactive dog class page with 12 transformation stories. That page went from my worst performer to consistently booking out 3 weeks in advance."
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#581c87;">— Certified dog trainer, suburban training studio</p>
      </div>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Start free</h2>
      <p>SocialProof is free forever for 1 active widget. Get testimonials on your most important page today with zero setup cost.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:2.5rem;text-align:center;">
        <a href="/signup" style="display:inline-block;background:#2563eb;color:white;padding:0.85rem 2.2rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
          Start collecting testimonials free
        </a>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#888;">Free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
      </div>
